{"tid":305394,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平離港忙清場　送別學生即走避暑　張曉明講話紅毯收一半","createTime":"2017-07-01T15:35:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-01T18:11:15.000Z","uid":39464,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"989a4f264d712d7ce5734afb8d75a56ad66a1b6e","tid":305394,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T15:35:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170701/s00001/e2045b92fa0ed18c6c81b48711ead2a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170701%2Fs00001%2Fe2045b92fa0ed18c6c81b48711ead2a7.jpg&h=3febdf55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國家主席習近平與夫人彭麗媛今午乘專機離港，於機場離開時，沒有發表講話。習近平離去後，烈日下曬了很久的歡送學生們也都怱怱離去，工作人員則忙着清場，紅地毯急急收起，至後來中聯辦主任張曉明講話時，地毯已捲起一半。<br />\n<br />\n現場保安嚴密，有十餘名俗稱「G4」的要員保護組成員，四周遠處亦見持槍的反恐特勤隊員戒備，而記者需經安檢後才可進入採訪區，但今次未有收起記者的毛巾和雨傘。<br />\n<br />\n習近平與彭麗媛步進機艙前，有回頭向歡送他的人士揮手道別，而習近平離港前於下車後及臨上機前均有跟新任特首林鄭月娥握手。<br />\n<br />\n而習近平進入機艙後，工作人員就立即帶領一班在場歡送主席的小學生離場，以免再有更多人中暑。<br />\n<br />\n習近平3日前抵港，當時有海外華文傳媒指該紅地毯太短，而今日所見的紅地毯，長度似乎一樣。習所乘坐的專機未離開時，已見有工作人員急急收起紅地毯，其後有工作人員發現中聯辦主任張曉明仍需發表講話，便立即把本已收起一半的紅地毯展開，因此張曉明講話時，背後有一張捲起了一半的紅地毯，整個過程亦被電視台直播。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170701/s00001/1498892653983\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170701%2Fs00001%2F1498892653983&d=AOliCmYgTrQQCVNHzCrRPMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=6552d28d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170701%2Fs00001%2F1498892653983&h=fdfd7c59\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170701/s00001/1498892653983</a>"},{"pid":"b60299f82c9ac1f85b4418c9b4d8da3c287c81cb","tid":305394,"uid":36029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T15:39:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d9f5f42bfa7dc4370c58b622a44f979dff86933","tid":305394,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T15:41:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80beaede0e30db79d53b461bd925b04fbce1952b","tid":305394,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T15:41:39.000Z","msg":"小明阻人收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0cac87c723246da27394b63fd1890c6b7d754bc","tid":305394,"uid":3773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T15:43:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小明阻人收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n工作人員：喂屌呢個茄呢啡乜水呀，嗱嗱聲過主啦"},{"pid":"5b023e217aceda0810041899a5d6e22941f70501","tid":305394,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T15:44:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小明阻人收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9b89011f4d2d152af7f5c9e9e37c7ab6c159c66","tid":305394,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T15:45:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"992d15393c32a0db949b9426160b05a87c552106","tid":305394,"uid":43173,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T15:51:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小明阻人收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n工作人員：喂屌呢個茄呢啡乜水呀，嗱嗱聲過主啦</blockquote><br />\n工作人員心諗:呢條契弟阻撚住收工,快D搵人一腳伸佢落台"},{"pid":"9981bffdb3b390fc7c7eec06148e29a617ade326","tid":305394,"uid":11753,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T15:51:17.000Z","msg":"夠鐘收檔喇過主啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"807a1e7d578a5646d457fe1eef70787c7394f259","tid":3053